                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="13036952" author="thejas" created="Fri, 20 May 2011 18:44:50 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;To fix this, the per-statement validation should be enabled only for interactive mode and if the -c option (check) is used.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13038097" author="rding" created="Mon, 23 May 2011 19:07:46 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;+1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13038206" author="thejas" created="Mon, 23 May 2011 21:37:31 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Unit test and test-patch passed. Patch committed to trunk and 0.9 branch. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13042460" author="daijy" created="Wed, 1 Jun 2011 22:43:33 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;PigServer.registerQuery() will not trigger validation after the patch, unless PigServer.setValidateEachStatement(true) is called.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
